Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是哈姆藏那家伙就生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈姆藏！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:05:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,响  真美来帮你抓住它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.37,0:05:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快出来吧  我会道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  那里有什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.38,0:05:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  有蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪…哪里  蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:23.01,up,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  真…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:28.64,Bann,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(418,0)\pos(495,0)\1c&E7DCD2&\3c&FFFFFF&}萩原雪步\N765事务所所属偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蟑螂在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪步怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:35.98,Bann,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(418,0)\pos(130,0)\1c&3396F4&\3c&FFFFFF&}高槻弥生\N765事务所所属偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:39.36,up,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}雪步请冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁快来把蟑螂…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  我已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪步  不能在茶水间地板上挖洞呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是快点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把蟑螂…  快把蟑螂从这里赶走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  哈姆藏是仓鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:05:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈姆藏？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上当了吧  真
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊织你又来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上当的人自己笨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…  真  伊织
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在拍你们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电视台的采访…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  这是有在拍摄的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  要早点说呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是水濑伊织  请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:39.34,Bann,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(417,0)\pos(130,0)\1c&E196FC&\3c&FFFFFF&}水濑伊织\N765事务所所属偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈姆藏  你已经被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投降出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.14,0:06:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  哈姆藏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.69,0:06:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  那么吵闹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是热闹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个要多少钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据容量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据大小不同价格不同吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.87,0:07:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(240,350)}这是算小的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,350)}容量是指记忆体…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好复杂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的  连我也会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:23.25,Bann,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(417,0)\pos(130,0)\1c&D35C23&\3c&FFFFFF&}如月千早\N765事务所所属偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  化妆占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个月的工作运只有一星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是恋爱运有三星呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.48,0:07:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:40.02,Bann,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(417,0)\pos(130,0)\1c&C03493&\3c&FFFFFF&}三浦梓\N765事务所所属偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思议的占卜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的会准吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:47.03,Bann,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(417,0)\pos(495,0)\1c&670EA5&\3c&FFFFFF&}四条贵音\N765事务所所属偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:49.20,fad1,NTP,0,0,0,,「相信占卜吗？」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  如果写的是好事的话就相信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵音的占卜呢  怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我坚信人生是靠自己去开拓命运的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命运是靠开拓出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.26,0:08:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定是这样呢  贵音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:10.80,up,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}哈姆藏你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:12.14,up,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}好像进这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:13.89,up,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}乖乖束手就擒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然跑到美希美希的那里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈姆藏也是男生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！  哈姆藏真H！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈姆藏！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了哈姆藏的食物真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.08,up,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}美希美希  摄像机哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:36.95,up,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}快说点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星井美希  初中三年级
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:46.71,Bann,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(417,0)\pos(135,0)\1c&42DFB0&\3c&FFFFFF&}星井美希\N765事务所所属偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  就这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太短了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.18,0:08:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有胸部很大哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  美希美希
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.06,0:09:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱睡的孩子长得大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这里人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  没听清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请再重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.24,0:09:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  大家给我适可而止！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:21.50,fad1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(290,350)\fad(500,501)}职业：
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:21.50,fad1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(340,350)\fad(500,501)}偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:29.00,frz,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(190,180)\fad(501,0)}歌唱课程\N(星井·天海·如月)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我呀  虽然还有很多不明白的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.98,0:09:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是觉得一点点慢慢来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.95,0:09:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美希做得不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:57.99,frz,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(190,200)\fad(0,0)}杂志采访「月刊偶像」\N(菊地·萩原)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.58,0:10:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之我对体力很有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想把舞蹈磨练得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想在电视里的歌唱节目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者大舞台上帅气地跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菊地君在女生中很有人气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为假小子的关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成这样都是爸爸害的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:26.85,up,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}因为他不让打扮得像个女生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天要突破爸爸那堵墙！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着吧  爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  萩原雪步小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不擅长和男性说话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么要成为偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我几乎没什么值得骄傲的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但却想成为偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…  是不是太天真了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你问我…  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想改掉畏缩的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是朋友又去帮我申请了面试…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然我还是不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个我听不清你在说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂雪步  快回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.74,0:11:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:18.16,frz,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(400,200)\fad(0,0)}CD大街贩卖&握手\N「太阳的嫉妒」(天海)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是天海春香  请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  律子小姐忙不过来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:30.42,fad1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(0,0)}音无小鸟  765事务所员工
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就像这样来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,300)}给  请看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:34.84,fad1,NTP,0,0,0,,「就像是兼任制作人吗？」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那样的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底只是帮忙而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好  我该去下个地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摄影师先生  春香就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:49.85,fad1,NTP,0,0,0,,「哎…！？」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:53.27,fad1,NTP,0,0,0,,「拜托了是…」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,300)}被拜托了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:55.82,fad1,NTP,0,0,0,,「哈…」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,300)}那就一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:11:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:00.95,fad1,NTP,0,0,0,,「噢  噢…」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:03.08,frz,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(190,170)\fad(0,0)}CHEX  LIVE  垫场\N15点入场  （如月）
Comment: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=========================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:09.33,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(208,209)}蒼い鳥　もし幸せ近く…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:09.33,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(208,209)}青鸟  如果幸福就在附近…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=========================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:17.97,fad1,NTP,0,0,0,,「对唱歌有什么想法吗？」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是什么样的歌曲  都想要认真对待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我不这样的话  对歌和对听众都会很失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:30.81,fad1,NTP,0,0,0,,「真的很喜欢唱歌呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.23,0:12:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,300)}是的  我只有唱歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以没时间玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经可以了吗  我想要集中下精神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我那样跳出去  还叫着「等下！」
